      "content": "While Powerhouse builds on blockchain principles, it diverges in a key way: blockchain's global consensus can limit speed and scalability. Powerhouse prioritizes local-first workflows, ensuring contributors can operate efficiently without requiring global synchronization. This is a deliberate architectural decision that trades global consistency guarantees for operational speed and contributor productivity in decentralized organizations.",
